{"tid":981062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肉圓父毆子網友動私刑 法界：私法正義不是正義","createTime":"2019-01-14T03:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T10:27:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5807ce004eda3aa813d140307e81683057accd","tid":981062,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"新北市永和區一間私立托嬰中心本月9日爆發老師涉嫌虐打幼童，12日蘆洲區又有一名父親見兒子買回的肉圓沒有加辣，暴怒把兒子掌摑倒地，媽媽衝過來救兒也被勒頸拖出房外暴打；二起事件都引發網友眾怒，前往事發地聚集動用「私法正義」，對此，新北地檢署資深檢察官指出「私法正義並不是正義」。<br />\n <br />\n檢察官認為，任何事件在沒有經過調查、沒有審視過所有證據、聽過被告解釋前，就單方面以眼前呈現的片段事實進行認定，甚至動用「私法正義」，這並不是正義；很悲哀的是，經過調查後，若檢察官或法官做出的處分或裁定，不符合網友先入為主認定的「正義」，司法官也會被認為是「不正義」。<br />\n <br />\n前新北地檢署、台北地檢署主任檢察官、明永法律事務所主持律師絲漢德指出，就網友動用「私法正義」所涉及的刑責來看，因均沒有阻卻違法事由如正當防衛或緊急避難；前往托嬰中心噴漆、丟雞蛋、持木棍徘徊，涉及的法律責任包括毀損、公然侮辱與恐嚇罪，前二樣是告訴乃論罪，恐嚇則是公訴罪。<br />\n <br />\n不過本案可以考量的事，若網友主張是因公益而義憤犯案，檢察官審酌其背後動機，也確實不是為了私怨犯案，即使網友面臨追訴，也有可能做出緩起訴或不起訴處分，即使送到法院評估也是輕判拘役或罰金等。<br />\n <br />\n另外，眾人聚集、闖入社區、動用私刑毆打家暴父，當事人可以提告包括傷害與侵入住宅等罪；本案因已實際成傷，當事人即使主張心生畏懼、提告恐嚇，也會被傷害行為吸收，檢察官僅會以傷害、侵入住宅來論處。<br />\n <br />\n絲漢德認為，兩案性質相近，網友都可以說是激於「義憤」，為了社會公益，但所謂義憤，一般是指當場看到不法事件，完全沒有辦法忍受，立即動手制止或制裁；兩案卻都是網友看了網路影片或新聞報導後，基於片段的呈現，跑去現場實施「私法正義」，並非現場直擊看到，是否適用有待承辦檢察官認定。<br />\n <br />\n資深檢察官表示，他並不是要為家暴父親說話，就新聞影片中呈現，該名父親確實非常可惡，但也無法排除父親主觀上確實是認為小孩在說謊，是出於管教而動手；雖然我國教育朝向零體罰方向，但父母對於孩子的管教權，是否完全不能實施體罰，以及合理的界線又在哪，有時真的「清官難斷家務事」。<br />\n <br />\n檢察官認為，本案目前網友已形成家暴父就是可惡、該死的先入為主判斷，假設將來經過調查，承辦檢察官做出不符合網友期待的處分結果，檢察官也將被評為「不正義」；但他仍想請民眾冷靜想想，沒有經過調查、審視所有客觀、對被告有利不利證據的「私法正義」，並不是正義。"},{"pid":"e06175614b51558c8d2a900065f296adfdd0a933","tid":981062,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"人治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要觀眾睇得開心"},{"pid":"25f04de3e8ef55ebfad4bb732bf977d61f38cbd0","tid":981062,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"片？"},{"pid":"d326997b5615998557f96a45768b89145fd5c248","tid":981062,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"多得台灣班垃圾法官單單都輕判話有得教化囉"},{"pid":"857fc83aaec9a2ecfa458208e0cd1ccaf573e2fa","tid":981062,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"單純睇依單野 私下打到佢爆丸 好正義喎"},{"pid":"5f3c610ddaaa99d8da367ff482f8d74136ce8a29","tid":981062,"uid":131345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkOXi3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkOXi3Q.jpg&h=26b75977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩係台仔LINE GROUP見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972d6e26a536e583cf83e62eeffb87f005bf8dcd","tid":981062,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f3c610ddaaa99d8da367ff482f8d74136ce8a29","tid":981062,"uid":131345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkOXi3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkOXi3Q.jpg&h=26b75977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩係台仔LINE GROUP見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e01bc4ecb74e440af13c2b56962fc050b49ec7c","tid":981062,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"係華人社會講程序正義只會畀人屌死"},{"pid":"a1f1e34ccc2202a36983ab5ec4f0b8e5934bc600","tid":981062,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣司法 笑話黎"},{"pid":"4cf529e03070f30643b9d168ad10fc5b243f22a2","tid":981062,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"幾百年前水滸傳已經寸緊法律撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柴進柴大官人，是個老壞老壞的人。仗著趙宋朝廷的丹書鐵券，神馬東西都往家裡攔，殺人放火的，坑蒙拐騙的，吃白食打秋風的，當然也有被逼的走投無路的如林沖等。不過他也有倒霉的時候，就是撞上五條杠的殷天錫之流。當他的朝廷恩賜抵不住現任長官的衙內時，李逵上場了！三拳兩腳滴，將殷天錫結果了性命。<br />\n<br />\n要說柴進此前也勸過李逵：<span style=\"color: red;\">殷天錫再來時，不要動手，先跟他打官司，因為有&ldquo;條例&rdquo;。可李逵回答道條例條例，依著條例，天下不亂了！我隻是先打后商量！</span>最終，打死了殷天錫，也把柴進送進了高唐州的死牢，后來還是梁山眾好漢一起出動，救下了大恩人柴進。<br />\n<br />\n本來，有條例在，可以先打官司。但當時的條例，隻是一紙空文而已，挂在嘴上的多，實行的少。一旦如此，天下豈能不亂？隻有拳頭先上來。若有人在此時還談什麼條例，隻是笑談耳！"},{"pid":"8b22493573ce9883374b95474f1f63026e43beba","tid":981062,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/170774790022623/posts/657671084666322/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F170774790022623%2Fposts%2F657671084666322%2F&d=NpX4VTY7G2nO%2FOekE%2B%2FaMDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f76f7938\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/170774790022623/posts/657671084666322/</a>"},{"pid":"ebe1db30c26a3e495e5d4d7bb725cc208d1c1290","tid":981062,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"該出手就出手"},{"pid":"62a2946fc4d5da3648096923e1f5100d8460aad9","tid":981062,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"華人社會好難識咩係法治<br />\n除非鬼佬殖民過"},{"pid":"878982b1414571a608530e82f0c9cf2bb350d2e4","tid":981062,"uid":192517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"又有d柒頭叻唔切<br />\n以為死跟法律文字先叫「法治」<br />\n法治精神係指任何人都平等受一樣既管束呀，法例有錯係可以改架！"},{"pid":"39700981c304424d0f95a0b0ddce1cee6d3c4b18","tid":981062,"uid":9502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"台仔講咗幾十年都話警察負責捉人<br />\n法官負責放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}